      "start_time": 12.74,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b9568a77-08e2-4dc5-a15c-f13d337a68bd",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "Yeah. Um I so my name's Brandon. Um I work with a dot com. We're an internet listing service and I was on your guys website and notice that you have uh Like a handful or so of apartments that are gonna become available soon. Not sure if it's uh that they're under construction or what the case might be, but I wanted to call introduce myself and and see if there might be an opportunity to grab maybe 10-15 minutes later on this week to discuss you know the vacancies and and what we can do to help get those filled."
