      "start_time": 46.8,
      "recording_attendee_id": "b10ad9de-d3d6-492e-b807-099fc90516b8",
      "order_number": 4,
      "text": "So what we've got here is we have kind of a unique animal. Um we have a bill to open a year ago and it's all senior housing. Um So what we are finding with senior housing is um that the print advertising is working pretty well and that we also um are working with Glenn Devon's um and then uh carrying dot com and senior housing that so we stick just with the senior products, unfortunately when we've got those products that are sort of more of an open market, uh we end up with a lot of leads from students because we're right across the street from Michigan"
    },
